       <script>
        var fullScreen = false;
     var MT;
     var MH;
 
     // Journey Parallax
 
     function homeJourney(direction) {
        
         if (mediaQuery('tablet') || mediaQuery()) {
             // Tablets and up
             $this = $(this).find('.container');
             $next = $(this).next('div[data-magellan-destination]').find('.container');
             $prev = $(this).prev('div[data-magellan-destination]').find('.container');
            
             // Find the rewards module for the next and this step
             var t_boxes = $this.find('.boxes');
             var n_boxes = $next.find('.boxes');
 
             if (mediaQuery('tablet') && ($(this).attr('id') == 'toddler-time')) {
                 $this.css('margin-top', '147px');
             }
 
         } else {
             // Mobile
             $id = $(this).attr('id');
             $this = $(this).find('div:not(.container) .bgkcustom');
             $next = $(this).next('div').find('div:not(.container) .bgkcustom');
             $prev = $(this).prev('div').find('div:not(.container) .bgkcustom');
         }
 
         if (direction == 'down') {
             $thisStep = $(this).next('div').data('magellan-destination');
             if ($thisStep == undefined) {
                 $thisStep = $('.journey div[data-magellan-destination]:last-child').data('magellan-destination');
             }
 
             if ($(this).attr('id') != 'toddler-time' && mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                 $this.fadeOut('fast');
                 $next.fadeIn('fast');
             }
 
         } else {
             $thisStep = $(this).data('magellan-destination');
             if (!$thisStep) {
                 $thisStep = $('.journey div[data-magellan-destination]:eq(0)').data('magellan-destination');
             }
 
             if (mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                 $this.fadeIn('fast');
                 $next.fadeOut('fast');
             }
         }
            
                
     }
 
     var journeyWaypoints = $('.journey div[data-magellan-destination]');
 
     $(document).ready(function () {
 
         $('.steps-menu a').on('click', function (e) {
             e.preventDefault();
             var scrollV,
             scrollH,
             $this = $(this),
             href = $this.attr('href');
             history.pushState({}, '', $(this).attr("href"));
         });
 
         //$("#back-top-wrapper").remove();
         $("#lang-select").chosen();
 
         resizeJourney();
 
         $('.enter_code').click(function () {
             var rewards_module = $(this).parents('.rewards_module');
             if ($(window).width() < 768 && $(window).width() > 640) {
                 rewards_module.css({
                     top: rewards_module.position().top,
                     marginTop: -rewards_module.height()
                 });
             }
             if (mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 10 }, "slow");
             }
             else if (mediaQuery('tablet')) {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 50 }, "slow");
             } else {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 120 }, "slow");
             }
         });
 
         $('.collapse_codes').click(function () {
             var rewards_module = $(this).parents('.rewards_module');
             rewards_module.css({
                 marginTop: 0
             });
         });
 
         // Initial set of the images
         $('.steps-menu ul li a').each(function (e) {
             if (e == 0) {
                 var img = $(this).attr('data-image-hover');
             } else {
                 var img = $(this).attr('data-image');
             }
             $(this).find('img').attr("src", img);
         });
 
         var steps = $('.steps-menu ul');
 
         $('#toddler-time').waypoint(function (direction) {
             // Journey Menu Sticky
             if (mediaQuery('desktop')) {
                 if (direction == 'down') {
                     var ST = steps.offset().top;
                     steps.removeClass('js-changed').css({
                         top: ST,
                         marginTop: 0
                     });
                     $('.steps-menu ul').removeClass('fixed');
 
                 } else {
 
                     steps.addClass('js-changed').css({
                         top: '50%',
                         marginTop: MT
                     });
                     $('.steps-menu ul').addClass('fixed');
 
                 }
             }
         });
 
         journeyWaypoints.waypoint(homeJourney, {
             offset: function () {
                 if (mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                     return -($(this).height() - ($('header').height() * 2));
                 } else {
                     return -((($(this).height()) + ($('header').height())) / 2);
                 }
             }
         });
 
         $('.add_more').click(function () {
             var rewards_module = $(this).parents('.rewards_module');
            
             $(this).parents('[data-magellan-destination]').addClass('expanded');
             journeyWaypoints.waypoint(homeJourney, {
                 offset: function () {
                     return -($(this).height());
                 }
             });
             if (mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 120 }, "slow");
             }
             else if (mediaQuery('tablet')) {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 200 }, "slow");
             } else {
                 $('html, body').animate({ scrollTop: rewards_module.offset().top - 120 }, "slow");
             }
         });
 
         $('.collapse_codes').click(function () {
             $(this).parents('[data-magellan-destination]').removeClass('expanded');
             journeyWaypoints.waypoint(homeJourney, {
                 offset: function () {
                     return -($(this).height());
                 }
             });
 
         });
 
         $('footer,header,.off-canvas-wrap').addClass("home");
 
         $('html,body').on('touchstart', function () {
             $('body').stop();
         });
     
     });
 
 
 
     $(window).on('load', function () {
         if (window.location.hash) {           
             var hash = window.location.hash.substring(1); //Puts hash in variable, and removes the # character 
             if (hash.indexOf("expecting-mom") >= 0)
                 hash = "expecting-mom";
             if (hash.indexOf("new-mom") >= 0)
                 hash = "new-mom";
             if (hash.indexOf("moving-baby") >= 0)
                 hash = "moving-baby";
             if (hash.indexOf("toddler-time") >= 0)
                 hash = "toddler-time";                
            
             gotoAnchor(hash, false);
             var item = $('a[href="#' + hash + '"]');
             item.addClass('active');            
               
         } else {
             var hash = 'expecting-mom';
             gotoAnchor(hash);
             var item = $('a[href="#' + hash + '"]');
             item.addClass('active');
         }
     });
 
     $(window).on('resize', function () {
 
         if (!mediaQuery('desktop') && heightChange() && fullScreen == false) {
             bgkcustom();
             fullScreen = true;
         } else {
             if ((!mediaQuery('desktop') && !heightChange()) || mediaQuery('desktop')) {
                 $('.js-changed').attr('style', '').removeClass('js-changed');
                 $('.steps-menu ul').removeClass('fixed');
                 resizeJourney();
 
                 var journeyWaypoints = $('.journey div[data-magellan-destination]');
                 journeyWaypoints.waypoint(homeJourney, {
                     offset: function () {
                         if (mediaQuery('mobile')) {
                             return -($(this).height() - ($('header').height() * 2));
                         } else {
                             return -((($(this).height()) + ($('header').height())) / 2);
                         }
                     }
                 });
 
             }
         }
 
         viewport_w = $(window).width();
         viewport_h = $(window).height();
 
     });
    
     //Added for the rocketfuel Integration- start
 
     $('document').ready(function () {
 
         $('.journey .steps-menu ul li:nth-of-type(n+5) a').removeAttr('data-magellan-arrival');
         if (mediaQuery('desktop')) {
             $('.journey').css('overflow-x', 'hidden');
 
         }
 
     });
 
 
     //Added for the rocketfuel Integration- End
       </script>

         var si_n_val = $(ele).closest("section.content").attr("id") == "join" ? 'wem_hug_signup_social;gigya_signin' : 'wem_hug_signin_social;gigya_signin';

     function SanitizeDrawerBox(v) {
         var pathRegex = /([.]{2}\\|[.]{2}\/)/;
         var blacklistRegex = /<(applet|body|embed|frame|frameset|html|iframe|img|style|layer|link|ilayer|meta|object|script)>/;
         var badwordArray = [''];
         var replaceString;
 
         var hasBadword = false;
 
         replaceString = v.replace(/(\r\n|\r|\n)/g, ' ');
         replaceString = replaceString.replace(/[()'",.\{\}\[\]]/gi, '');
         replaceString = replaceString.replace('%', '');
         replaceString = replaceString.replace('&', '');
         replaceString = replaceString.trim().toLowerCase();
 
         for (var i = 0, len = badwordArray.length; i < len; ++i) {
 
 
             if ((replaceString.indexOf(' ' + badwordArray[i].toLowerCase() + ' ') != -1)
            || ((badwordArray[i].length == replaceString.length) && replaceString.indexOf(badwordArray[i].toLowerCase()) == 0)
            || ((replaceString.lastIndexOf(' ' + badwordArray[i].toLowerCase()) != -1) && (replaceString.lastIndexOf(' ' + badwordArray[i].toLowerCase()) == (replaceString.length - (badwordArray[i].length + 1))))
            || ((replaceString.indexOf(badwordArray[i].toLowerCase() + ' ') == 0))
            ) {
                 hasBadword = true;
 
             }
 
             if (hasBadword) break;
         }
 
         return ((v.match(pathRegex) == null) && (v.match(blacklistRegex) == null) && !hasBadword);
 
     }
     function getQueryByName(name) {
         name = name.replace(/[\[]/, "\\[").replace(/[\]]/, "\\]");
         var regex = new RegExp("[\\?&]" + name + "=([^&#]*)"),
             results = regex.exec(document.createTextNode(location.search).textContent);
         if (results == null) {
             results = '';
         }
         if (!SanitizeDrawerBox(results.toString().toLowerCase())) {
             results = "";
         }
         return results === null || results == '' ? "" : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, " "));
     }

     function getCookie(cname) {
         var name = cname + "=";
         var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
         for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
             var c = ca[i];
             while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') c = c.substring(1);
             if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
         }
         return "";
     }

     function GetURLParameter() {
